        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Made of smooth, white wood, this staff is capped at each end with a golden cross adorned with a multitude of ruby cabochons. A staff of healing grants an item bonus to the Hit Points you restore anytime you cast the heal spell using your own spell slots or using charges from the staff.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells.</p>\n<p>The item bonus granted to <em>heal</em> spells is +1.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrip</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Stabilize]</em></li>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Heal]</em></li>\n</ul>"
